	* sawfish/wm/commands.jl (define-command): spec and type args
	are now keyword parameters

	* sawfish/wm/workspace.jl, sawfish/wm/windows.jl,
	sawfish/wm/viewport.jl, sawfish/wm/swapper.jl,
