	* x-cycle.jl (x-cycle-next): ignore windows with never-focus
	set, for obvious reasons

	* raise-commands.jl (raise-or-pass-through-click): new function

	* workspace.jl (window-menu): fix bug when calling make-label
	for sticky windows

